window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"I love a good story especially if it can make me laugh, cry, cheer, and a host of other emotions. So far in this series, I have hit them all.\" </p> <p>Europe is erupting is tension and violence. </p> <p>David is only adding to the conflagration by setting a trap, one that our team will trip to save those people still alive. </p> <p>There is one thing every enemy of Bethany Anne finds out. They will be ground down under her heels. </p> <p>Series includes: </p> <p><i>Death Becomes Her - The Kurtherian Gambit 01</i> </p> <p><i>Queen Bitch - The Kurtherian Gambit 02</i> </p> <p><i>Love Lost - The Kurtherian Gambit 03</i> </p> <p><i>Bite This - The Kurtherian Gambit 04</i> </p> <p><i>Never Forsaken - The Kurtherian Gambit 05</i> </p> <p><i>Under My Heel - The Kurtherian Gambit 06</i> </p> <p><i>Kneel or Die - The Kurtherian Gambit 07</i> - Mid Mar 2016 </p>"; 
